RACE.FOOTNOTES: EL CHUMELITO ran off pace from the leader then coming three wide around the turn took advantage of being on the outside and took off with a late drive to catch and pass the leader by the wire. ELDORADO DREAM started in the middle of the pack then quickly took the lead with a comfortable length between the other foes, continued to hold the distance between the foes until the last fifty yards where they got caught. FLAT FAST started off in the back of the pack then slowly made some ground in the turn but still in the back, and coming on to the stretch that made a strong rally to over take foes coming from the back to make the show position by the wire. OUR VALLEY ran in the middle of the pack had a slight gain on the turn then evened out on the stretch. HIT A NOTE ran in the front of the pack early but shuffled back then evened out after the turn. ZENFULLY ZESTY ran with an even pace throughout the race moving around tired foes on the stretch. EMPEROR'S CHOICE ran in the front of the pack then coming in to the turn started to fall back but by the end of the turn they faded back thru the stretch. PHANTOMOFTHEOPERE blew from the gate then quickly fell back to last, they trailed until the sixteenth pole where they finally passed a tired foe. PRINCESS JAYLEEN ran at the front of the pack but started slowing before the turn, just ran out of gas coming down the stretch. THIS RACE WAS HAND TIMED.
